explanation.summary: Kt qu in tm  cho thy nhp tim ca bn nhanh hn mc bnh thng (nhp nhanh), nhng cc ng dn in trong tim vn hot ng n nh.
explanation.details: Hnh nh sng in tim cho thy cc nhp p ca tim din ra u n v nhanh. C th, nhp tim ca bn l 106.21 ln/pht, cao hn gii hn bnh thng (60-100 ln/pht). Tuy nhin, thi gian dn truyn in tim qua cc bung di ca tim (phc b QRS) ch l 0.056 giy (56 mili giy). Theo hng dn y khoa, phc b QRS hp (< 0.12 giy) cho thy tn hiu in c dn truyn qua cc ng thng thng trong tim mt cch hiu qu, khng c s tc nghn ng k hoc bt thng t cc bung di ca tim. Ch s bin thin nhp tim (HRV RMSSD) l 10.696 ms, thp cho thy s linh hot ca nhp tim c th b gim i, thng thy trong cc trng hp nhp tim nhanh.
explanation.recommendations: Bn nn ngh ngi, th gin v trnh cc yu t kch thch nh c ph, tr m hoc cng thng. Ht th su c th gip lm chm nhp tim.
explanation.next_steps: Tip tc theo di nhp tim ca mnh khi ngh ngi. Nu nhp tim vn duy tr trn 100 ln/pht khi  th gin hon ton, hoc nu bn cm thy au ngc, kh th, chng mt, hy thm khm bc s chuyn khoa tim mch  c t vn v kim tra k hn.
